## Part 4 – Institutional Applications

### Application A: Capability Lens – Marine Insurance Trust Market (SIM F)

This section will present a detailed case study of the Trust Framework
applied to a multi-agent marine insurance market. The SIM F model
implements contribution, trust, credibility, credit, coordination,
coexistent systems, and continuation in a single simulation engine.

(Full technical specification and data: see Applications/CapabilityLens/SIM_F/)
